> **Why**: The user is not a developer. They will run the app from the terminal and report back whatever error text they see. Having every possible error pre-documented means the user can search this document for the error message and find the cause + fix immediately, without needing to understand the code.

### MANDATORY: Tooltip & Help Protocol

> **All implementing agents MUST follow this protocol when creating UI controls:**
