## 10. RISK MITIGATIONS

| Risk | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|--------|-----------|
| Out of memory on long videos | Crash | Streaming extraction. Memory estimation + warning. Sampling rate. |
| Disk full on Cuboid Fill | Crash | Show estimated disk usage before generation. |
| 3D preview crash on huge textures | VTK error | Cap textures at 2048×2048. Preview is optional. |
| Rings output impossibly large | Memory/disk | Cap at RINGS_MAX_OUTPUT_DIAMETER (8192px). Auto-sample mode. |
| PyInstaller bundle too large | Distribution | Exclude unused Qt modules. SAM2 is separate optional install. |
| Slow scrubber seeking | Bad UX | Debounce 200ms. Sequential read for generation. |
| VTK/PyVista texture issues | Bad preview | Fallback: use individual textured planes instead of single box mesh. |
| Cross-platform differences | Bugs | Test macOS + Windows at end of each phase. |
| Codec not supported | Can't load video | OpenCV FFmpeg backend handles most. Show error dialog for unsupported. |
| User draws empty slit-tear | Crash | Validate at least one line drawn before generation. |

